	(28, 1, '2020-06-19 00:40:21', '2020-06-18 22:40:21', '<div class="textDesc">\n<p class="textDescTitle">Main Features</p>\n<p class="textDescContent">Redmi 9\nGlass front (Gorilla Glass 5), plastic back, plastic frame\nDual SIM (Nano-SIM, dual stand-by)\nSplash resistant\nIPS LCD capacitive touchscreen, 16M colors\n6.53 inches, 102.9 cm2\n1080 x 2400 pixels, 20:9 ratio (~403 ppi density)\nCorning Gorilla Glass 5\nOS Android 10, MIUI 12\nChipset Mediatek Helio G80 (12 nm)\nCPU Octa-core (2x2.0 GHz Cortex-A75 &amp; 6x1.8 GHz Cortex-A55)\nGPU Mali-G52 MC2\nCard slot microSDXC (dedicated slot)\nInternal 32GB 3GB RAM, 64GB 4GB RAM\nQuad 13 MP, f/2.2, 28mm (wide), 1/3.1", 1.12µm, PDAF\n8 MP, f/2.2, 118˚ (ultrawide), 1/4.0", 1.12µm\n5 MP, f/2.4, (macro)\n2 MP, f/2.4, (depth)\nFeatures LED flash, HDR, panorama\nVideo 1080p@30fps\nSingle 8 MP\nFeatures HDR\nVideo 1080p@30fps\nLoudspeaker Yes\n3.5mm jack Yes\nWLAN Wi-Fi 802.11 a/b/g/n/ac, dual-band, Wi-Fi Direct, hotspot\nBluetooth 5.0, A2DP, LE\nGPS Yes, with A-GPS, GLONASS, GALILEO, BDS\nInfrared port Yes\nRadio Wireless FM radio (no wired headphones required)\nUSB 2.0, Type-C 1.0 reversible connector, USB On-The-Go\nSensors Fingerprint (rear-mounted), accelerometer, gyro, proximity</p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="sizeDesc js-sizeDescription">\n<p class="sizeDescTitle">Specification</p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="imageDesc">\n\n<img class="js-descLazyload lazy-loaded" src="https://des.gbtcdn.com/storage/item/6602611330169458688/15916/4af955bc77ae.jpg" data-lazy="https://des.gbtcdn.com/storage/item/6602611330169458688/15916/4af955bc77ae.jpg" data-was-processed="true" />\n\n<img class="js-descLazyload lazy-loaded" src="https://des.gbtcdn.com/storage/item/6602611330169458688/15916/157ccd1d58c5.jpg" data-lazy="https://des.gbtcdn.com/storage/item/6602611330169458688/15916/157ccd1d58c5.jpg" data-was-processed="true" />\n\n<img class="js-descLazyload lazy-loaded" src="https://des.gbtcdn.com/storage/item/6602611330169458688/15916/6fc2a93037f0.jpg" data-lazy="https://des.gbtcdn.com/storage/item/6602611330169458688/15916/6fc2a93037f0.jpg" data-was-processed="true" />\n\n<img class="js-descLazyload lazy-loaded" src="https://des.gbtcdn.com/storage/item/6602611330169458688/15916/6e96604b76d6.jpg" data-lazy="https://des.gbtcdn.com/storage/item/6602611330169458688/15916/6e96604b76d6.jpg" data-was-processed="true" />\n\n<img class="js-descLazyload lazy-loaded" src="https://des.gbtcdn.com/storage/item/6602611330169458688/15916/5444078c2fac.jpg" data-lazy="https://des.gbtcdn.com/storage/item/6602611330169458688/15916/5444078c2fac.jpg" data-was-processed="true" />\n\n<img class="js-descLazyload lazy-loaded" src="https://des.gbtcdn.com/storage/item/6602611330169458688/15916/1c8c44082412.jpg" data-lazy="https://des.gbtcdn.com/storage/item/6602611330169458688/15916/1c8c44082412.jpg" data-was-processed="true" />\n\n<img class="js-descLazyload lazy-loaded" src="https://des.gbtcdn.com/storage/item/6602611330169458688/15916/1effed8601f5.jpg" data-lazy="https://des.gbtcdn.com/storage/item/6602611330169458688/15916/1effed8601f5.jpg" data-was-processed="true" />\n\n<img class="js-descLazyload lazy-loaded" src="https://des.gbtcdn.com/storage/item/6602611330169458688/15916/41721d375142.jpg" data-lazy="https://des.gbtcdn.com/storage/item/6602611330169458688/15916/41721d375142.jpg" data-was-processed="true" />\n\n<img class="js-descLazyload lazy-loaded" src="https://des.gbtcdn.com/storage/item/6602611330169458688/15916/44ac7fee0517.jpg" data-lazy="https://des.gbtcdn.com/storage/item/6602611330169458688/15916/44ac7fee0517.jpg" data-was-processed="true" />\n\n<img class="js-descLazyload lazy-loaded" src="https://des.gbtcdn.com/storage/item/6602611330169458688/15916/b516a4572b08.jpg" data-lazy="https://des.gbtcdn.com/storage/item/6602611330169458688/15916/b516a4572b08.jpg" data-was-processed="true" />\n\n<img class="js-descLazyload lazy-loaded" src="https://des.gbtcdn.com/storage/item/6602611330169458688/15916/2cc2d67c6898.jpg" data-lazy="https://des.gbtcdn.com/storage/item/6602611330169458688/15916/2cc2d67c6898.jpg" data-was-processed="true" />\n\n<img class="js-descLazyload lazy-loaded" src="https://des.gbtcdn.com/storage/item/6602611330169458688/15916/79b0d8a6980c.jpg" data-lazy="https://des.gbtcdn.com/storage/item/6602611330169458688/15916/79b0d8a6980c.jpg" data-was-processed="true" />\n\n<img class="js-descLazyload lazy-loaded" src="https://des.gbtcdn.com/storage/item/6602611330169458688/15916/93c57b5f5d9b.jpg" data-lazy="https://des.gbtcdn.com/storage/item/6602611330169458688/15916/93c57b5f5d9b.jpg" data-was-processed="true" />\n\n<img class="js-descLazyload lazy-loaded" src="https://des.gbtcdn.com/storage/item/6602611330169458688/15916/c5e4a91fd7eb.jpg" data-lazy="https://des.gbtcdn.com/storage/item/6602611330169458688/15916/c5e4a91fd7eb.jpg" data-was-processed="true" />\n\n</div>', 'Redmi 9', 'Redmi 9\nGlass front (Gorilla Glass 5), plastic back, plastic frame\nDual SIM (Nano-SIM, dual stand-by)\nSplash resistant\nIPS LCD capacitive touchscreen, 16M colors\n6.53 inches, 102.9 cm2\n1080 x 2400 pixels, 20:9 ratio (~403 ppi density)', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '23-autosave-v1', '', '', '2020-06-19 00:40:21', '2020-06-18 22:40:21', '', 23, 'http://localhost/Ecom/2020/06/19/23-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
	(29, 1, '2020-06-19 00:45:09', '2020-06-18 22:45:09', '<h2 class="goodsDescribe_title">Xiaomi Redmi Note 9S Descriptions</h2>\r\n<div class="product_pz">\r\n<h4 class="desc_title"></h4>\r\n<div class="product_pz_info mainfeatures desc_simp"><b>The Performance Beast</b>\r\nThe Redmi Note 9S offers a truly beast performance in every department. This smartphone features an impressive 48MP Quad Camera Array that combines a powerful 48MP primary sensor, a 8MP ultra-wide angle lens, a 5MP macro lens and a 2MP macro lens, so you are ready to click in any condition. Powered by the Qualcomm® Snapdragon™ 720G, gaming is effortless and efficient. Work and play uninterrupted with the huge 5020mAh battery that is accompanied by the 18W Fast Charger.\r\n\r\n<b>Main Features:</b>\r\n• <b>Rear camera photography:</b> ultra nightscape mode, AI scene detection, smart ultra-wide angle mode, ultra wide-angle edge distortion correction, AI beautify, burst mode, tilt-shift, level display, custom watermark, pro mode, portrait mode background blur adjustment, studio lighting, panorama mode, AI high-resolution photos.\r\n• <b>Front camera photography:</b> panorama selfie, palm shutter, AI silhouette detection, wide-angle distortion correction, front camera HDR, front camera display brightness correction, selfie timer, face recognition, age recognition, full screen camera frame, AI beautify, AI feature adjustment, AI makeup, AI portrait mode, AI scene detection, AI studio lighting.\r\n• With a <b>5020mAh large battery</b>, there is no need to charge frequently, and it is easy to cope with the needs of taking photos and playing games for a long time.\r\n• The battery can be charged in no time with the <b>18W charger</b> that is included in-box.\r\n• The Aura Balance design blends fashion and function, with the addition of <b>Corning® Gorilla® Glass 5</b> and <b>P2i splash-proof nano coating</b>.\r\n• Click sharp and clear self portraits on the powerful <b>16MP selfie camera</b>.\r\n• Enjoy a cinematic viewing experience with the <b>16.9cm (6.67) FHD+ DotDisplay</b> that features an in-display selfie camera and a stunning resolution.\r\n• Have enough and more room for all your essentials with the <b>512GB expandable storage</b>.\r\n\r\n<b>Rear Camera</b>\r\n48MP Quad Camera Array\r\n48MP primary camera: 1/2.25 inch CMOS image sensor, 1.6μm 4-in-1 super pixel, f/1.79\r\n8MP ultra-wide angle camera: 1.12μm, f/2.2, FOV 119°\r\n5MP macro camera: 1.12μm, 2cm focus distance\r\n2MP depth sensor: 1.75μm\r\nZoom: 10x digital zoom, PDAF, single-tone flash\r\n\r\n<b>Rear Camera Video</b>\r\nShort video editing, ultra-wide angle video recording, macro video recording\r\n4K recording - 30fps\r\n1080P recording - 60fps / 30fps\r\n720P recording - 30fps\r\n1080P ultra-wide angle video recording - 30fps\r\n720P ultra-wide angle video recording - 30fps\r\n1080P slow motion recording - 120fps\r\n720P slow motion recording - 960fps / 240fps / 120fps\r\n\r\n<b>Front Camera</b>\r\n16MP Front Camera: 1μm\r\n\r\n<b>Front Camera Video</b>\r\nFront camera video beautify, short videos (speed adjustment beauty filters and popular music)\r\n1080P/ 720P recording - 30fps\r\nSlo-mo video recording - 120fps\r\n\r\n<b>Both Cards Can Access 4G Connectivity Simultaneously</b>\r\nNanoSIM + NanoSIM + Micro SD\r\nMicro SD expandable up to 512GB\r\nTriple slot tray\r\nSupports 4G + / 4G / 3G / 2G\r\nSupports dual SIM VoLTE HD calling②\r\n\r\n<b>Network &amp; Connectivity</b>\r\nGSM: B2/3/5/8\r\nWCDMA: B1/2/4/5/8\r\nTDD LTE: B38/40\r\nFDD LTE: B1/2/3/4/5/7/8/20\r\n\r\n<b>Wireless Network</b>\r\nSupports protocols: 802.11a/b/g/n/ac\r\nSupports 2.4G Wi-Fi / 5G Wi-Fi\r\nSupports 2 x2 WiFi MIMO\r\nWi-Fi Direct / Wi-Fi Display\r\nSupports Bluetooth 5.0\r\nSupport VoWiFi\r\n\r\n<b>Notes:</b>\r\n1. Dual 4G SIM requires the support of local telecom operator services, and may not be available in all region.\r\n2. Due to the epidemic, postal services in some countries are suspended, delivery will be delayed, but most regional logistics are still smooth.\r\n\r\nTip:\r\n<b>Unlocked for worldwide use. Please ensure local area network is compatible. <a href="https://www.gearbest.com/blog/how-to/country-based-mobile-phone-network-frequency-bands-coverage-guide-1144" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">click here</a> for network frequency of your country. Please check with your carrier / provider before purchasing this item.</b></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="product_pz">\r\n<h4 class="expand_en_name">Specification</h4>\r\n<div class="product_pz_info product_pz_style2">\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>General</th>\r\n<td>Language: Azerbaijani,Malay,Bosnian,Catalan,Czech,Danish,German,Estonian,English(India),English(United Kingdom),English(United States),Spanish(Spain),Spanish(America),Basque,French,Galician,Hausa,Croatian,Indonesian,Italian,Latvian,Lithuanian,Hungarian,Maltese,Dutch,Official Norwegian,Uzbek,Polish,Portuguese(Brazil),Portuguese(Portugal),Romanian,Albanian,Slovenian,Slovak,Finnish,Swedish,Vietnamese,Turkish,Greek,Belarusian,Bulgarian,Kazakh,Macedonian,Russian,Serbian,Ukrainian,Georgian,Armenian,Hebrew,Urdu,Arabic,Persian,Nepali(India),Nepali(Nepal),Marathi,Hindi,Assamese,Bengali(India),Bebgali(Bangladesh),Punjabi,Gujarati,Oriya,Tamil,Telugu,Kannada,Malayalam,Thai,Khmer,Korean,Japanese,Chinese Simolified,Punjabi,Gujarati,Oriya,Tamil,Telugu,Kannada,Malayalam,Thai,Khmer,Korean,Japanese,Chinese Simplified,Chinese Traditional(Taiwan),Chinese Traditional(Hongkong)\r\nService Provider: Unlocked\r\nSIM Card Slot: Dual Nano SIM,Dual Standby\r\nSIM Card Type: Dual Nano SIM\r\nType: 4G Smartphone</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Hardware</th>\r\n<td>CPU: Snapdragon 720G\r\nCores: 2.3GHz,Octa Core\r\nExternal Memory: TF card up to 512GB ( not included )\r\nGPU: Adreno 618</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Network</th>\r\n<td>Network type: FDD-LTE,GSM,TDD-LTE,WCDMA\r\nWIFI: 2.4G/5G WiFi,802.11a/b/g/n/ac wireless internet,WiFi Direct,WiFi Display\r\nWireless Connectivity: A-GPS,Bluetooth,GPS,WiFi</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Display</th>\r\n<td>Screen resolution: 2400x1080\r\nScreen size: 6.67 inch\r\nScreen type: Corning Gorilla Glass 5,HDR</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Camera</th>\r\n<td>Back-camera: 48MP ultra-high resolution primary camera + 8MP ultra wide-angle + 5MP macro + 2MP depth\r\nCamera Feature: Night mode | Document mode | Cinematic portraits 48MP HD | Smart ultra-wide angle mode | Rear camera Beautify Steady handheld night photography | Portrait mode background blurring | Panorama mode Pro mode | Photo timer | Leveling | Burst mode | Face recognition | HDR | Ultra wide-angle edge distortion correction | Custom watermark | AI watermark | Kaleidoscope Portrait mode background blur adjustment | Full screen frame Rear camera AI scene detection (27 recognizable tags) | Macro camera\r\nCamera type: Four Rear Cameras and One Front Camera\r\nFlashlight: Yes\r\nFront camera: 16MP\r\nVideo recording: 4K Video,Support 1080P Video Recording,Support 720P Video Recording</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Other Features</th>\r\n<td>Additional Features: Alarm,Bluetooth,Calculator,Calendar,GPS,Notification,Side Fingerprint Sensor\r\nBluetooth Version: Bluetooth 5.0\r\nGoogle Play Store: Yes\r\nI/O Interface: 2 x Nano SIM Slot,3.5mm Audio Out Port,Microphone,Speaker,Type-C\r\nWaterproof / Water-Resistant: No\r\nOTA: Yes\r\nSensor: Accelerometer,Ambient Light Sensor,E-Compass,Fingerprint Sensor,Gyroscope,Infrared Radiation,Proximity Sensor,Z-axis linear vibration motor</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Battery</th>\r\n<td>Battery Capacity (mAh): 5020mAh\r\nBattery Type: Non-removable</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Package Contents</th>\r\n<td>Cell Phone: 1\r\nPower Adapter: 1\r\nSIM Needle: 1\r\nUSB Cable: 1\r\nUser Manual: 1\r\nProtective Cover: 1</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Dimensions and Weight</th>\r\n<td>Product weight: 0.2090 kg\r\nPackage weight: 0.5500 kg\r\nProduct size (L x W x H): 16.58 x 7.67 x 0.88 cm / 6.53 x 3.02 x 0.35 inches\r\nPackage size (L x W x H): 18.00 x 10.00 x 6.00 cm / 7.09 x 3.94 x 2.36 inches</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="nomargin">\r\n<div class="nomargin">\r\n<div class="self-adaption"><img class="js-descLazyload lazy-loaded" title="Xiaomi Redmi Note 9S Smartphone The Latest Smart Phone of Redmi Series Global Version EU Plug - White 6GB + 128GB" src="https://des.gbtcdn.com/uploads/pdm-desc-pic/Electronic/image/2020/03/31/20200331145729_49603.jpg" alt="Xiaomi Redmi Note 9S Smartphone The Latest Smart Phone of Redmi Series Global Version EU Plug - White 6GB + 128GB" data-lazy="https://des.gbtcdn.com/uploads/pdm-desc-pic/Electronic/image/2020/03/31/20200331145729_49603.jpg" data-was-processed="true" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="self-adaption"><img class="js-descLazyload lazy-loaded" title="Xiaomi Redmi Note 9S Smartphone The Latest Smart Phone of Redmi Series Global Version EU Plug - White 6GB + 128GB" src="https://des.gbtcdn.com/uploads/pdm-desc-pic/Electronic/image/2020/03/31/20200331145729_66599.jpg" alt="Xiaomi Redmi Note 9S Smartphone The Latest Smart Phone of Redmi Series Global Version EU Plug - White 6GB + 128GB" data-lazy="https://des.gbtcdn.com/uploads/pdm-desc-pic/Electronic/image/2020/03/31/20200331145729_66599.jpg" data-was-processed="true" /></div>\r\n<div class="self-adaption"><img class="js-descLazyload lazy-loaded" title="Xiaomi Redmi Note 9S Smartphone The Latest Smart Phone of Redmi Series Global Version EU Plug - White 6GB + 128GB" src="https://des.gbtcdn.com/uploads/pdm-desc-pic/Electronic/image/2020/03/31/20200331145729_79073.jpg" alt="Xiaomi Redmi Note 9S Smartphone The Latest Smart Phone of Redmi Series Global Version EU Plug - White 6GB + 128GB" data-lazy="https://des.gbtcdn.com/uploads/pdm-desc-pic/Electronic/image/2020/03/31/20200331145729_79073.jpg" data-was-processed="true" /></div>\r\n<div class="self-adaption"><img class="js-descLazyload lazy-loaded" title="Xiaomi Redmi Note 9S Smartphone The Late